# Agent memory index

One fact per file. Subfolders by memory type:

- `daily/` — session notes, `YYYY-MM-DD.md`
- `project-memory/` — durable per-project state
- `constraints/` — hard rules the user has set
- `preferences/` — how the user likes things done
- `observations/` — atomic observations (`memory_type: observation`)
- `relations/` — links between entities (`memory_type: relation`)
- `lessons-learned/` — postmortems and corrections

Every note carries `doc_type: agent_memory` frontmatter and starts life as
`review_status: unreviewed`. A human promotes durable knowledge into
`30-curated/` — agents never do that themselves.
